        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer808704798" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer748962196399039177"><b>Be sure to visit my <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4729956-crystal-craig?shelf=favorites' rel='nofollow noopener'>Favorites Shelf</a> for the books I found most entertaining.</b><br/><br/>Jamie Ford&apos;s, <i>Hotel on the Corner of Bitter and Sweet</i> lived up to my expectations. This book has a title that begs you to pick it up. It&apos;s about history and culture and music. But, like most love stories that take place during war times - there&apos;s sadness and heartbreak.</span>
  <span id="freeText748962196399039177" style="display:none"><b>Be sure to visit my <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/4729956-crystal-craig?shelf=favorites" rel="nofollow noopener">Favorites Shelf</a> for the books I found most entertaining.</b><br /><br />Jamie Ford's, <i>Hotel on the Corner of Bitter and Sweet</i> lived up to my expectations. This book has a title that begs you to pick it up. It's about history and culture and music. But, like most love stories that take place during war times - there's sadness and heartbreak.</span>
  <a data-text-id="748962196399039177" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
