<div id="review_377831496" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/377831496" />
    <a title="Miz" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6907245-miz"><img alt="Miz" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1420153794p2/6907245.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/377831496?book_show_action=true">Jul 26, 2012</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Miz" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Miz" href="/user/show/6907245-miz">Miz</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="ebook 9780345512505" href="/book/show/6358094-hotel-on-the-corner-of-bitter-and-sweet">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6907245-miz?shelf=historical">historical</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6907245-miz?shelf=ebook-owned">ebook-owned</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6907245-miz?shelf=romance">romance</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6907245-miz?shelf=favourites-5-stars">favourites-5-stars</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6907245-miz?shelf=tearjerker">tearjerker</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer377831496" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8116663810640261924">Wow, just wow. This book was masterfully told and while it started slow, it built into a crescendo of feelings and emotions. The character development was amazing, the storyline outstanding, and the writing masterful.<br/><br/>Recommend this. Pick it up, read it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


